casebody.data:
GASKINS
v.
DAIL 398P15-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 17, 2017 Kathleen N. Bolton, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Samuel L. Gaskins, for Gaskins, Samuel Lee

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 16th of November 2017 by Petitioner to Reconsider Order Denying Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of November 2017."
